oji\" />上次新城市<br />\n班狗最多咪叫4點個班頂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:08:20.000Z","msg":"今次係無衝突之下,佢夠膽入以後唔洗做生意"},{"pid":"9b079f4ba8f37e803c9f4f0d750d3cc2ba981059","tid":1556465,"uid":83504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:16:05.000Z","msg":"喺商場唱歌都驚，都要咁樣自我審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共港共同班狗咪就係想你咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0cc30239f6e3d9d51d243970747b4fcc18a410c","tid":1556465,"uid":82238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:38:05.000Z","msg":"係咪今日搞得太成功 要開始出招叫人唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a8f12d63d858268da14a448faf9bdc534b26f1","tid":1556465,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:41:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mme1QAAF9ms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMme1QAAF9ms&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNqZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=9c28a60d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mme1QAAF9ms</a><br />\n<br />\n原曲：高地大教堂 Highland Cathedral<br />\n填詞：Hans J&uuml;rgensmeyer<br />\n2019年版詞：法蘭西多士<br />\n演奏：黑暗超夢夢<br />\n演唱：自由香港合唱團<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自由港 未怕海浩瀚<br />\n自強不朽 是我海岸<br />\n太平山 做我等助佑<br />\n敦我克己奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n勇武香港 眾民處變不驚<br />\n盡每分光 光顯社稷威名<br />\n無懼戰鬥 無懼捨生獻命<br />\n縱使犧牲 自由自可戰勝"},{"pid":"c3562171ee0ae1384162469e10c7cec32f8aee0f","tid":1556465,"uid":190332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:43:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f05a2b80787472c8c93c66f7f8bcff2f67b8fce","tid":1556465,"uid":190332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T20:44:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08288a6d75f97d30ac013abf741c51170f108ad8","tid":1556465,"uid":89